# Toolchain manifest — order matters. Comment out (#) to skip.
#
# Failure policy:
#   HARD — abort install: sync_dotfiles, missing lndir, unknown CLI flags
#   SOFT — warn and continue: CUSTOM tools, PKG installs, cursor hook without jq
#
# CUSTOM <name>  — fnm, pnpm, rustup, tmux-manager (lib/tools/*.sh)
# PKG <pkg> <cmd> [brew-pkg]
#   pkg      — yay/pacman package (Linux)
#   cmd      — binary to check on PATH
#   brew-pkg — homebrew formula (defaults to pkg)

CUSTOM fnm
CUSTOM pnpm
PKG ripgrep rg
PKG fd fd
PKG neovim nvim
PKG jq jq
PKG go go
CUSTOM rustup
CUSTOM tmux-manager
LINUX PKG ydotool ydotool
